{"tid":1613034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《都市日報》獲日資全面收購 今起不於港鐵派報章","createTime":"2019-10-02T12:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T03:33:53.000Z","uid":68738,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"469e63c94cb06c7fc049cf313c78e1a53b644420","tid":1613034,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:15:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191002/large/1570017613_6c8c.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191002%2Flarge%2F1570017613_6c8c.jpg&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX25ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=2ca208e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191002/large/1570017613_6c8c.jpg</a><br />\n《都市日報》於港鐵站免費派發17年，今起因賣盤而結束派報<br />\n<br />\n《都市日報》社長、都市新聞多媒體執行主席李永康向員工發佈內部通告，表示今天剛收到日本買方的通知，已確定全面收購都市新聞多媒體，於今個月內確定所有交收及重組細節，並於11月底前交易完成。另由今天開始，《都市日報》不會再在港鐡沿線站內派發報紙，而會重新規劃地面上的派發點，但網絡版業務將繼續。<br />\n<br />\n該內部通告指出，《都市日報》為配合買家的商業模式及發展方向，未來業務將包括數碼媒體、網上購物、會員積分禮遇以及大數據分析、預測等等，通告未有提及報章業務。<br />\n<br />\n《都市日報》於2002年4月15日創刊，逢周一至五早上於港鐵站及繁忙地點免費派發。該報原由瑞典傳媒集團Kinnevik創辦並於2002年在香港發行，據官網數據顯示，《都市日報》每日平均發行量為40萬份。商人黃浩在2013年以2億元收購該報股份，並擔任《都市日報》母公司都市新聞多媒體主席一職。黃其後在2017年以4億元作價，將都市新聞多媒體售予資深傳媒人兼商人蕭作利。蕭作利於今年1月已表示確認都市新聞多媒體獲收購一事，指準買家已簽約及交付訂金，當時更裁員30人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191002/60110190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60110190&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX25ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=9d5270e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60110190&h=c682dced\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191002/60110190</a>"},{"pid":"fd822a3d1f74f629917ea4157e59d09025b47679","tid":1613034,"uid":13349,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.metrodaily.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2019-09-08_23-46-04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F2019-09-08_23-46-04.jpg&h=11ff8dbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5472b0142a34abf5d8852d6dee733fb3bd17b410","tid":1613034,"uid":65716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"咪撚再做共狗"},{"pid":"35ae6be49ff099903412b88441d74c2e2c59f0cb","tid":1613034,"uid":119271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54da34483fc1d9d67784cd556cd2eebafe1468e6","tid":1613034,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49cf9d36034dd9f7c1e8fff9f65369cf48b5a9a","tid":1613034,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:18:23.000Z","msg":"日資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8759444b70fcc711ac992721f07b01fe9812d319","tid":1613034,"uid":18484,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:18:49.000Z","msg":"日資係咩公司先<br />\n一陣好似某間支那雜貨鋪咁扮日本人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbd1edbb074a7422b11e7aaa0fb7934e3825929","tid":1613034,"uid":25601,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"共匪在日資產買都市日報ja"},{"pid":"bc352847844102c58a71ac47c916505d8b7c8d47","tid":1613034,"uid":276839,"like"